GateDocument.TextWithNodes: While the Indian army has become rock - solid in the western front, and has developed the capability of withstanding any Pakistani adventure in that sector, it has become highly vulnerable in its eastern sector, where its enemy is not a national army but a multitude of secessionist, terrorist and drug - running militants operating between Southeast Asia and northeastern India through Bangladesh.
